name: Itzal
description: Designed for quick clandestine attacks, the Itzal Archwing excels at striking from the darkness of space.

abilities.name: Arch Line
abilities.description: Launch a tethered hook that either pulls enemies close, or pulls the Warframe toward any stationary objects it hooks onto.

abilities.name: Penumbra
abilities.description: Activates a cloaking field that hides the Warframe and any nearby allies who remain stationary.

abilities.name: Cosmic Crush
abilities.description: Forms a miniature black hole that sucks in all nearby objects before rupturing in a massive shock wave.

abilities.name: Fighter Escort
abilities.description: Deploys drones that fight alongside the Warframe, each detonating in a destructive blast when killed.

languages.description: Der Itzal Archwing wurde für schnelle, lautlose Attacken konzipiert und schlägt aus der Dunkelheit des Alls zu.
languages.name: <ARCHWING> Itzal

languages.description: Conçue pour de rapides attaques surprises, l'Archwing Itzal excelle dans le combat spatial en frappant depuis les zones obscures.
languages.name: <ARCHWING> Itzal

languages.description: Ideata per rapidi attacchi furtivi, l'Archwing Itzal eccelle nel colpire i nemici nell'oscurità dello spazio.
languages.name: <ARCHWING> Itzal

languages.description: 재빠른 은신 공격을 위하여 설계된 잇잘 아크윙은 우주의 어둠에 스며들어 기습할 때에 가장 뛰어난 성능을 보입니다.
languages.name: <ARCHWING> 잇잘

languages.description: Diseñadas para realizar rápidos ataques furtivos, el archwing Itzal destaca golpeando desde la oscuridad del espacio.
languages.name: <ARCHWING> Itzal

languages.description: （英文：ITZAL）专为隐匿行动而打造，这架曲翼擅长在太空的黑暗中进行突袭作战。
languages.name: <ARCHWING> 刺影

languages.description: Разработанный для скрытых атак, Итзал предназначен для нападений из тьмы космоса.
languages.name: <ARCHWING> Итзал

languages.description: 素早い隠密攻撃のために開発されたこのアークウイングで、宇宙の暗闇からいきなり急襲をかけることができる。
languages.name: <ARCHWING> Itzal

languages.description: Zaprojektowany do skrytych, precyzyjnych uderzeń, Archwing Itzal jest doskonały do nagłych, niespodziewanych ataków.
languages.name: <ARCHWING> Itzal

languages.description: Projetada para furtividade e capacidade de manobrar, esta Archwing excede em seus golpes vindos da escuridão do espaço.
languages.name: <ARCHWING> Itzal

languages.description: 專為隱匿行動而打造，這架 Archwing 擅長在太空的黑暗中進行突襲作戰。
languages.name: <ARCHWING> Itzal

languages.description: Itzal Archwing ออกแบบมาเพื่อการลอบโจมตีอย่างรวดเร็ว โดดเด่นในการโจมตีจากด้านมืดของอวกาศ
languages.name: <archwing> Itzal

languages.description: Hızlı ve gizli saldırılar için dizayn edilen Itzal Archwingler uzayın karanlık noktalarından saldırmayı sevenler için.
languages.name: <ARCHWING> Itzal

languages.description: Арквінґ «Ітцаль» розроблений для швидких потаємних нападів. Ідеально підходить для раптових атак із темряви космосу.
languages.name: <ARCHWING> Ітцаль
